author: "Firmicus Maternus, Julius"
title: "Iulii Firmici Materni Iunioris Siculi v.c. Ad Mavortium Lollianum, Astronomic[o]n libri VIII / per Nicolaum Prucknerum astrologum nuper ab innumeris mendis vindicati. His accesserunt, Claudi Ptolemaei [apotelesmaton] quod Quadripartitum uocant, lib. IIII."
